comments: Gordon (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Irving (BOS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Ross (ORL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Brown (BOS) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown (BOS) and does not deliver contact.
On contact in the post between Hayward (BOS) and Vucevic (ORL) off ball, Gordon makes slight contact with Vucevic in the post.
Irving (BOS) makes contact to Gordon's (ORL) body but the contact is marginal and does not affect his shot at the rim.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and does not deliver contact.
Fournier (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Irving (BOS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Augustin (ORL) makes elbow to head/neck area contact with Irving (BOS) during his drive to the basket which affects his ability to defend.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Carter-Williams (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ross (ORL) and Brown (BOS) engage and disengage off-ball.
Carter-Williams (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Hayward (BOS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Gordon (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Morris (BOS) at the start of the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Morris (BOS) lifts his pivot foot.
Carter-Williams (ORL) makes contact to the body of Morris (BOS) at the end of the drive but the contact does not affect his ability to release the pass.
Vucevic (ORL) gives Theis (BOS) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
On contact between Brown (BOS) and Carter-Williams (ORL) during the rebound, Brown makes hand to arm contact during the rebound.
Carter-Williams (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Hayward (BOS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Carter-Williams (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Morris (BOS) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Fournier (ORL) has a collapsed arm to his body when he makes minimal contact with Irving (BOS) after Irving's shot attempt.
Morris (BOS) dislodges Carter-Williams (ORL) from his position during the rebound.
Fournier (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Irving (BOS) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) straddles the lane line and remains in the lane for more than three seconds without actively guarding an offensive player.
Hayward (BOS) remains in the lane for more than three seconds without actively guarding an offensive player.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
